mixin range(id)
    label(class="range-lable label mrg-top-30") 
        span(class="range-lable__name")
            | диапазон цены
        p
            span(class="range-lable__cost min", data-cost="min")
                | 5 000₽ 
            span(class="range-lable__cost")
                | -
                | 
            span(class="range-lable__cost max", data-cost="max")
                | 10 000₽
    div(class="range mrg-top-20", id=`${id}`)
        div(class="range__left-point", data-btn="button2")
        div(class="range__between")
        div(class="range__right-point", data-btn="button1")
    p(class="range-text mrg-top-20") Стоимость за сутки пребывания в номере